com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata

Class DetailEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.DetailEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDetailEntry
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InternalDetailEntry

    public class DetailEntry
extends Object
implements IDetailEntry
    Standard implementation of IDetailEntry useful for passing into methods like IDetailUpdate.changeDetail or IDepthUpdate.changeDepth (as used in StandardInstrument).

    This is designed for efficient reuse. Call clearMarketDataItems method to empty out any current data and then use again.

        public IMarketDataItem[] getMarketDataItems()
        Description copied from interface: IDetailEntry
        Gets all market data defined for this entry.

        The entire array should not be processed. Process until a null is encountered or an entry with fieldID == 0.

        Specified by:
